In the above example, our lambda would not be implicitly constexpr in C++17 but it would be in C++20 (asstd::count_ifwas made constexpr in C++20). This means in C++20 we can makefiveLetterMonthsconstexpr:constexpr auto fiveLetterMonths{ std::count_if(months.begin(), months.end(),
